#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Select program at on the footer bar</h2>
This select shows you what program you are running, allowing
you to change to other programs you have access to on the
Brightsands server.
<p>
More importantly, the "logout" option turns off browser access to
any of the software on this server without re-issuing an account and password.
